                 <p>
                    Skiing in Pahalgam's snowy terrain is a wonderful experience. After Gulmarg, this is one of the best places to go skiing during the winter months.<br />
                    Aru is a luxury ski area located near Pahalgam center. Skiing is a lot of fun because of the beautiful surroundings and tranquil atmosphere.<br />
                    In January and February of each year, a large snow celebration is held. This event includes a variety of adventure activities such as horseback riding, skiing, and sledding.

                 </p>
