              <p>
                  Pahalgam offers a variety of hiking trails and serves as a base camp for many hikers. Pahalgam's lush green mountain ranges, lakes, and virgin meadows make it ideal for all types of trekking.<br />

                    The best time to go trekking in Pahalgam is from April to June. Consider trekking:<br />
                    Tarsar Marsar Lakes - 4 to 7 days<br />
                    Kolahoi Glacier Trek - 8 to 9 days<br />

                    Pahalgam to Sonmarg - 6 to 7 days<br />
                    Opt for short and day treks as well
